Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.44,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.60,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.16,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.30,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:22.65,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:27.38,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:34.32,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not home yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nanako-san, there's a letter for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... it's from Henmi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What! Really? Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! A big envelope! I wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Nanako-san, how have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I must apologize for not writing very often...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm enclosing the brochure for our Gakuin University Fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...and if it appeals to you, please do plan to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any formal invitations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...in fact, they told us to invite all the women we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a rumor that there are prizes for all the women.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So please bring your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,P.S.—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,P.S. These days, I don't hear from you quite as often.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume "no news is good news".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm happy you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,20. The Gardening Shears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are clubs for English, comedy, anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! All kinds of music ensembles too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's lots of food stands, also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Mariko-san will want to go too, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a masquerade dance too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be wearing a mask. Then you could even hold hands in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"There are many masks to choose from"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take this one, "Snow White".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This one, "Juliet".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-woo! Then you'll meet a "Romeo"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The University Fair? There's a dance party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How utterly disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? What's so disgusting about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A man and woman holding hands, bodies touching...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking about it gives me the creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're twisted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's twisted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I can't let you go to such a repulsive affair alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me back that program!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now see here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Give it back! That's Nanako's!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this program that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That you're dating a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That he's a student at Gakuin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen. This guy is like a brother to Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like he's her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Like" a brother, right? Not actually her brother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What business is it of yours who she associates with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well well! Now it's obvious that something's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't catch me hanging out with you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in asking her to go with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...'cause she can't stand being near "disgusting" places!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just too big a risk for you two to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's far too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to protect Misonoo-san from the hands of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. I'll protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what time and where do we meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...everyone is looking forward to the Fair this Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Takada's "International Relations"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I have that book too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! I've looked all over, but it's out of print.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sell it to you, but you can borrow it as long as you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The brakes don't feel quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. You know where my room is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on in while I check these out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Fukiko-san... It's been a while! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking care of the roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your roses are always so gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... not very talkative, is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She must not like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah. Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first met her she was in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she's a lovely young woman. Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she's an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever goes on in her head, it's a complete mystery to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not join us for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no thanks. I have things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you haven't been here since you graduated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you invite your high-schooler to the fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I sent her a program.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she's coming, and plans to bring a couple of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Girls usually enjoy university fairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:10:01.37,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yoshino naru, natsumi no kawano kawa yodo ni, kamo no naku naru yamakage ni shite...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.70,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,What focused vision this poem has!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.46,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,It is so suggestive, idyllic, and eloquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.22,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Note the many "N" syllables used in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:14.35,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,It might have been too plain without that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never know unless you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, over there! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And ending that as "yamakage ni shite" is so suggestive, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Kaoru-no-Kimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama... I have a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A message?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, on behalf of Misonoo Nanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A message?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, on behalf of Mariko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:11:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san would like you to come to the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The University Fair? Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd love to have you and Kaoru-no-Kimi go with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here I am asking you for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Nanako-san is asking Kaoru-no-Kimi for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking Kaoru to go to a fair at Gakuin University...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Um... but what's so funny about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The odds are probably ten thousand to one. There's no way she'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Best you don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Also... I appreciate the offer, but I can't go either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gakuin Fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I know a graduate student there... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... we have another scrimmage on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Mariko-san will miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can forget, because I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can forget, because I loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's some tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Nanako go to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think the pearls would go perfectly with this dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For sure it would!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, would you lend them to me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's only a university fair! Why a necklace?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Just one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In the upstairs dresser, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Walking on air, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how she feels about Takehiko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We should let her know soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not brave enough for that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know I'll have to, someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Misonoo residence...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to call so late. I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any plans for tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... yes. In the afternoon... with Shinobu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good! Could you spare some time in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A tea ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I have a tea ceremony every Sunday morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I invite one of the Sorority members.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems everyone is busy tomorrow... so I'd like to invite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, would you? Come to my house tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll be free tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful for the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! I'm sure it will be lovely, just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't mention this to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've invited a freshman to a tea ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand. Some others might feel jealous about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. And good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I forgot to tell you something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you come over to my house, could you stop at the Sorority?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the storage room there? Please pick up the {\i1}Meissen{\i0} tea set.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Meissen{\i0} tea set?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... a special set just for special guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to use it for our ceremony tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The key is at the security desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorority members can always pick it up from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, now....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,See you then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One o'clock sharp at Reuben's, in front of the university. okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. Be on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If the tea ceremony finishes by 11:30; I can make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The key to the Sorority's storage room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign your name and grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a member of the Sorority, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's see... a {\i1}Meissen{\i0} tea set...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This one... is a {\i1}Seiburu{\i0} soup set...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all in boxes which look alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is beyond me... I should have gotten more details...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's locked! How on earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange. The door couldn't have locked itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Who locked the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door! Stop playing games!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I know you're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door! Please, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's doing this? Open up! Please open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stay locked up in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll miss the tea ceremony and the university fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! There's someone out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't go! Help me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay there until evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Tomoko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid you were all waiting for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...but Nanako still isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her 5 more minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's charge her 100 Yen for each minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I won't be at the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And how will I be able to apologize to Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working far too hard for a Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And you? You're smoking far too much for a Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd promise to quit smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you went to the Gakuin University Fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Her program!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll have a little fair just for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Fukiko, there's a phone call...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's from Misonoo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:22:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry. I can't apologize enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.57,0:23:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi broke the lock and then she...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.68,0:23:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this happened! I'm sorry I missed everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I had no idea. What an experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have the tea ceremony some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't keep Shinobu-san and the others waiting. Enjoy the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, enjoy it! Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:14.16,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:19.63,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:25.24,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.24,0:24:30.71,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.45,0:24:36.99,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.99,0:24:42.46,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.46,0:24:45.19,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.19,0:24:48.00,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.00,0:24:50.40,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.40,0:24:55.67,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.22,0:25:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, Tomoko, and Mariko go to the Gakuin University Fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.66,0:25:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There, Mariko is determined to protect Nanako from all the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.07,0:25:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako becomes upset when she discovers how little she knows about Henmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.91,0:25:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: The University Fair
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.79,0:25:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
